      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum linear-elastic model with frictional contact appropriate for F1717 quasi-static compression-bending regime; model form uncertainty quantified via comparison to published analytical estimates.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic continuum model with isotropic Ti-6Al-4V material properties and frictional contact (μ=0.3) at screw-rod and screw-block interfaces. Model form appropriate for quasi-static loading below yield. Sensitivity to friction coefficient assessed; QoI variation < 3% over μ range 0.2–0.4. Gradation 3 achieved."
