      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from certified material test reports for the specific Ti-6Al-4V lot used in bench specimens; geometric dimensions measured from representative production hardware.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa) and yield strength (880 MPa) from certified material test reports. Geometric dimensions from CMM measurements of five production screws; dimensional variability < 0.5% CV. Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (n=1000); 95th percentile QoI uncertainty < 4%. Gradation 3 achieved."
