      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories (FDA OSEL and DePuy Synthes internal). All specimens from same production lot; CMM verification confirms dimensional conformance. Inter-laboratory coefficient of variation for stiffness 3.1%, yield force 4.7%. Gradation 3 achieved."
