      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions replicate ASTM F1717 protocol with documented control of crosshead speed, fixture alignment, and environmental conditions across both laboratories.",
      "rationale": "Single test condition per ASTM F1717 protocol (5 mm/min crosshead speed, ambient temperature). Environmental controls documented but only one loading rate explored; no variation in test temperature or fixture pre-load investigated. Gradation 2 achieved against required Gradation 3. Identified as known gap; accepted given medium model risk and convergent inter-laboratory results.",
