      "rationale": "One-to-one traceability established between FEA input parameters and specimen characterization data. Material properties from same lot as test specimens; geometry from CMM measurements of same production batch. Boundary condition fidelity confirmed by comparing fixture compliance in FEA against measured machine compliance. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
