    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-cou1-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3 due to single-condition testing; this gap is accepted given medium model risk level, convergent inter-laboratory results, and the conservative nature of the single test condition relative to clinical loading. All three primary QoIs satisfy quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96; percent difference < 10%). Overall credibility package supports Accepted decision for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw FEA model in the defined COU.",
